cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SD 

This paper deals with sentiment analysis of comments related to the Rohingya movement, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves classification and analysis of data, which falls under sub-categories such as cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CY (Computers and Society). Finally, the paper also involves data mining and statistical analysis, which falls under cs.SD (Software Development).
